******variable*****
no need to type
it can be number,string, boolean
it is case sencetive like it's false not false

we can use "" or """ for string
for length of a string use len() function

print(string_var[0]) this will give first inde value
print(string_var[-1])this will give the last inde value

print(string_var[0:3]) first 3 string(0 1 2 '3 is not included')
print(string_var[0:]) not error it will give all the string
print(string_var[:3])first 3 string
print(string_var[:]) full string

